<section begin=hpregenintro /><dfn>Health Regeneration</dfn> determines the amount of health a unit regains each second. It is shown as a small number with a <code>+</code> sign at the right side of the unit's health bar.

Heroes also gain bonus health regeneration based on their {{Attribute ID|strength}}. Each point of strength increases the hero's health regeneration by {{Attribute bonuses|bonus health regeneration flat}}<sub>HP</sub>.<section end=hpregenintro />

Health regeneration heals the unit in 0.1-second intervals. This rate cannot be changed by anything. Health regeneration has no cap.

Health regeneration is affected by [[health regeneration manipulation]]. When increased or reduced, the HUD shows the increased/reduced values.

