===Items===
Note that these tables only account for the items' passive traits. They do not include bonuses provided by item abilities (i.e. {{A|Headdress|Regeneration Aura}}).

Items that provide regeneration bonus by flat rate and {{Attribute ID|strength}}:
{{#lpdb:datapoint
